title: Hear Anthraxs Fast Thrashy Frantic New Song Evil Twin
text:
Hear Anthrax's 'Fast, Thrashy, Frantic' New Song, 'Evil Twin' 
Rolling Stone Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Anthrax guitarist Scott Ian says the band's new single, "Evil Twin," deals with "my relationship to the violence perpetrated by radical extremists."
